    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Wildfire_Channel_HttpHeaders flushes on postDispatch meaning that I can't log from my dispatchLoopShutdown plugins. Moving the flush to a new dispatchLoopShutdown method in Zend_Wildfire_Channel_HttpHeaders allows logging to Firebug in the normal manner.</p>

